name: Miguel Rodriguez
summary: Miguel Rodriguez is a 32 year old Mechanical Engineer based in Los Angeles, California. Originally from San Diego, he holds a graduate degree from University of Southern California. Being bilingual, he speaks both English and Spanish. He values hard work, compassion, and family ties. His interests include traveling, cooking, and hiking. A Catholic by religion and moderate in politics, Miguel is interested in a monogamous, long-term relationship. He identifies as a straight man who uses he/him pronouns. Though he doesn't have children, he wants to have a family in the future. He's also a proud dog owner. Taurus by zodiac sign, an ISTJ in MBTI personality type, Miguel leads an active lifestyle. He occasionally drinks but does not smoke or use marijuana and drugs. Miguel is seeking a partner aged between 24 and 35, who shares similar lifestyle habits and wants to have children in the future.
